---
// Problems section component
---

<!-- Problem Section -->
<section id="problem" class="text-brand-text">

  <!-- Grid columns -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-0">

    <!-- Left Column Problem -->
    <div class="text-center py-20 sm:py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 xl:py-28 px-6 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 bg-[#e7e5e0] flex flex-col">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8 md:mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <p class="font-sans mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-charcoal-500 text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
          The Problem
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-tight mb-3 sm:mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-tight px-4 sm:px-0">
          Tired of "AI overwhelm"?
        </h2> 

        <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-sans leading-relaxed px-4 sm:px-0"> 
          AI promised simplicity but delivered complexity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-left px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-0 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <p class="mb-4 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
          You've spent hours experimenting with ChatGPT prompts, downloading automation apps, and 
          watching tutorials that promise to "revolutionize" your business — yet nothing seems to stick.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
          You're not alone. Most real estate professionals are stuck between curiosity and chaos — 
          excited about AI's potential but frustrated by the tech jargon, wasted time, and lack of practical results.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
          At 4RealtyAI, we get it. You don't need another shiny tool or trendy platform. You need clarity — a clear strategy, systems that actually work, and guidance from people who understand both real estate and technology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column Solution -->
    <div class="text-center py-20 sm:py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 xl:py-28 px-6 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 bg-brand-primary flex flex-col">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8 md:mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <p class="font-sans mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-charcoal-500 text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
          The Path Forward
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-tight mb-3 sm:mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-tight px-4 sm:px-0">
          Let's make AI actually make sense
        </h2> 

        <p class="text-center text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-sans max-w-3xl leading-relaxed px-4 sm:px-0"> 
          4RealtyAI bridges the AI gap
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-left mb-6 sm:mb-8 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-0 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <p class="mb-4 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
          Here's the deal: AI doesn't have to be complicated. You don't need to learn how to "code" or 
          memorize endless prompts. You just need someone who can connect the dots for you.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
          That's what we do at 4RealtyAI. We sit down with you, look at how your business runs, and 
          pinpoint exactly where AI can save you time and increase your income.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-0 text-left max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-brand-text leading-tight mb-4 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6">
          In just 5 days, we will:
        </h3>
        
        <ul class="font-sans space-y-2 sm:space-y-2.5 md:space-y-3 text-left text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 sm:gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-charcoal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Identify your biggest AI opportunity</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 sm:gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-charcoal-200 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Implement the right solution</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 sm:gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-charcoal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Train your team to use it</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 sm:gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-charcoal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Track real business results</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
